      "value": "<h4>Item Modification (Wristpad)</h4>\n <p>When you are forced to make a Constitution saving throw to maintain concentration on a power you can use your reaction and spend 2 tech points to automatically succeed on the saving throw.</p>\n<p>You can only spend a number of tech points in this way equal to your proficiency bonus. You regain the ability to do so when you complete a long rest. </p>\n<p>You can use Refocused Subroutine even if you have already used a different Subroutine modification during the casting of the power.</p>",
